subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Jeff Withey of Kansas, a former volleyball player, blocked 10 shots against North Carolina State on Friday, and Sunday he’ll turn his attention to North Carolina 7-footer Tyler Zeller.
